name: Approaching the bridge
description: Abstract glitch art made with AnaCam and Vaporgram on the good old HTC Incredible S with custom unofficial CyanogenMod 11 firmware (Android 4.4.4. KitKat). Based on a photo of an old pedestrian bridge across the Tysmenytsia River taken on an HTC Incredible S with AnaCam (available at f-droid.org), additional effects were applied using the standard  gallery app and Vaporgram (available in Play Market). 1125x1500 px. Author: Mkriiis.
